            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the Greek cheese is in the oven, wash your <strong>gem</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>outer</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces and shred the <strong>inner</strong> <strong>core</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1681806467758-x200.jpg",
