      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> to the quick-pickled shallot with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>mustard & shallot dressing</strong></p>",
