    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained potatoes </strong>and <strong>drained butter beans</strong> to the bowl with the dressing</p><p>Add <strong>half </strong>the<strong> chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>pumpkin</strong> <strong>seeds </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Mix it all together – this is your <strong>potato & butter bean salad</strong></p>",
