    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the<strong> torn lettuce </strong>and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> with the <strong>potato & butter bean salad</strong>, then spoon the <strong>spicy ‘Nduja baked Greek cheese </strong>over the top</p><p>Drizzle over any <strong>remaining spicy ‘Nduja marinade</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped parsley</strong> and <strong>remaining pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
